title: Is EA About To Bring Back Dead Space? - Kinda Funny Games Daily 06.21.21
description:
Blessing and Tim talk about the return of Dead Space, the return of Cyberpunk 2077, and the return of PSX.

Time Stamps - 
00:00:00 - Start
00:02:02 - Housekeeping
There’s a new Kinda Funny Podcast up right now featuring Billy West AKA the voice of Doug, Fry from Futurama, Bugs Bunny and more! Check out that episode on Youtube.com/KindaFunny and on podcast services around the globe.
Something you can only get on Youtube though are Roger’s edits! This morning over on the Youtube channel you can catch Roger’s edited version of Nick and Snowbike Mike’s playthrough of Operation Tango. Go check that out over on Youtube.com/KindaFunnyGames.
Thank you to our Patreon Producers: Donavan Harkness & Black Jack
The Roper Report  -
00:03:35 - Is EA About to bring back Dead Space??? - Tom Phillips @ Eurogamer
00:19:38 - Cyberpunk is back on the PlayStation store
00:23:05 - PlayStation Experience May Be Making a Comeback in 2021 - Richard Warren @ GameRant
00:33:10 - Ad
00:38:20 - Tekken X Street Fighter is officially canceled - Michael McWhertor @ Polygon
00:44:20 - That Abandoned PlayStation App has been delayed by 3 days
00:51:12 - Out today
